==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gelatinize
<hw>Ge*lat"i*nize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>To convert into gelatin or jelly. Same as <er>Gelatinate</er>,
<pos>v. t.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Photog.)</fld> <def>To coat, or otherwise treat,
with gelatin.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gelatinize</ent>⟦br⟧

